schools.name: Manhattan Middle School Of The Arts And Academics

data.description: First time on the market since originally built in 1966!  Don't miss this rare opportunity to own this conveniently located gem backing up extensive city of Boulder open space & East Boulder Rec Center!  This 5 bedroom, 3 bathroom home borders natural beauty and offers ease in access to both recreation and the necessities of life.  Near Bobolink Trailhead and subsequent trail system, East Boulder Recreation Center, shopping, local restaurants, BVSD and private schools and more!  While completely comfortable to live in, bring your dreams for updating its original condition.  It's common to see raptors and beautiful wildlife in the open space right from the kitchen window!
